          %li.mypage__container__box__content__upper__menu__right
            %h3.mypage__user__todo
              %a.mypage__user__todo__link{href:""}
                やることリスト
        .mypage__container__box__content__upper__list
          %ul.mypage__container__box__content__upper__list__news
            %li.mypage__container__box__content__upper__list__news__flame
              %a.mypage__news{href:""}
                %figure.mypage__mercari__logo
                  %img{:alt => "", "data-src" => "//static.mercdn.net/images/mercari_profile.png", :src => "//static.mercdn.net/images/mercari_profile.png"}/
                .mypage__news__body
                  .mypage__news__body__text
                    《まもなく終了！》今なら最大”P1500”もらえる！詳しくはこちらから♪
                  %time
                    %i.mypage__clock__icon
                      ●
                    %span
                      22時間前
                %i.mypage__click__icon
                  >
            %li.mypage__tab__list__btn
              %a.mypage__tab__list__btn__text{href:""}
                一覧をみる
